To run this code create a main project directory and inside it create a sub directory called templates and put all html files in it and create another file app.py in the main directory.

/your_project_directory
│
├── app.py
└── templates
    ├── index.html
    └── result.html

Create a virtual enviornment and activate it.
install all the dependencies using the following command:-
pip install Flask pydicom Pillow numpy opencv-python
